Episode 1: Pilot
It's difficult to take a group photo where no one looks bad, and almost impossible to take one where everyone looks their best. The "Cheese App" (previously titled "Stitch") fixes this by letting users choose their favorite take for each individual, and "stitching" them together in one optimal frame.
